---
title: Huevos Rancheros with Fried Eggs, Guacamole, Cheese & Lime Crema
description: If you're a fan of breakfast for dinner, this is 100% the meal for you! Get ready for our spin on the classic Mexican breakfast of warm tortillas loaded with creamy refried black beans, topped with savory tomato sauce and eggs fried just the way you like them. Dollop it all with guacamole, drizzle with tangy lime crema, then sprinkle with a blend of Mexican cheeses and crisp scallion greens (and hey, you might just want it for breakfast, too!)
